  "description": "<b>9年前，时任美国总统乔治・W・布什曾计划推出全国性的监视政策，但是司法部和联邦调查局的高管却认为此举违法，因而威胁要辞职。</b>据《华盛顿邮报》<a href=\"http://www.washingtonpost.com/investigations/us-surveillance-architecture-includes-collection-of-revealing-internet-phone-metadata/2013/06/15/e9bf004a-d511-11e2-b05f-3ea3f0e7bb5a_story.html\" target=\"_blank\">报道</a>，在布什授意美国国家安全局(NSA)开始收集境内电子邮件和Skype呼叫的元数据之后，代理检察长James Comey、联邦调查局局长Robert Mueller、以及司法部的高层领导，便从2004年3月起着手起草辞职信。<br /><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d600649/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241370.htm&amp;t=%E5%B8%83%E4%BB%80%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%9B%BE%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD%E6%80%A7%E7%9B%91%E8%A7%86%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD+%E5%A4%9A%E9%83%A8%E9%97%A8%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%82%E5%A8%81%E8%83%81%E8%A6%81%E7%A6%BB%E8%81%8C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241370.htm&amp;t=%E5%B8%83%E4%BB%80%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%9B%BE%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD%E6%80%A7%E7%9B%91%E8%A7%86%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD+%E5%A4%9A%E9%83%A8%E9%97%A8%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%82%E5%A8%81%E8%83%81%E8%A6%81%E7%A6%BB%E8%81%8C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241370.htm&amp;t=%E5%B8%83%E4%BB%80%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%9B%BE%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD%E6%80%A7%E7%9B%91%E8%A7%86%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD+%E5%A4%9A%E9%83%A8%E9%97%A8%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%82%E5%A8%81%E8%83%81%E8%A6%81%E7%A6%BB%E8%81%8C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3